Looking for a Jeep Cherokee near Washington?

The Jeep Cherokee is a compact SUV with a tradition of competitive pricing and strong off-road capability starting at just under $24,000. While the Cherokee and its competitors are often offered with all-wheel drive, the Cherokee offers more aggressive off-roading equipment, such as a locking rear differential. With the largest selection of cars from dealers and private sellers, Autotrader can help find the perfect Cherokee for you.

Autotrader has 2,501 Jeep Cherokees for sale near Washington, DC, including a Certified 2015 Jeep Cherokee 4WD Limited, a Certified 2015 Jeep Cherokee 4WD Limited w/ Luxury Group, and a Certified 2015 Jeep Cherokee FWD Limited w/ Luxury Group.

Not sure if a Cherokee is the right fit for you?

That's okay! We make it easy to shop for your next vehicle by body type, mileage, price, and much more.You can find other popular Jeep vehicles such as Wrangler, Grand Cherokee, and Gladiator on Autotrader.
